{"tid":28860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本人建議全港密閉及室內地方清拆冷氣及通風系統","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T15:01:16.000Z","uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5301cd430a75c70ba31c8f993636c63a21fbacc8","tid":28860,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"原因以下有三<br />\n一.<br />\n香港位於亞熱帶地區，本地居民對寒冷天氣感到不適<br />\n<br />\n二.<br />\n本港冬季持續介乎於19至25度，氣溫異常寒冷，使用冷氣會做造成不必要的浪費。<br />\n<br />\n三.<br />\n香港人普遍患鼻敏感，通風系統會令群眾感到不安，焦慮，神經緊張，影響日常生活。密閉的環境能令患者得以舒緩。"},{"pid":"e3c6430d4c1d69c32ac4b2cc857be922d8282d38","tid":28860,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b1798d78481fdfadb820955996c73e07c0f08a","tid":28860,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"食屎啦你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}